         <abstract id="aspace_214584ad552fd80c92ed7f687bc30178">Correspondence, photographs, clippings and memorabilia of the Meyer family of Ada, Ohio documenting family activities during World War I. The five brothers, all Yale graduates, served overseas.</abstract>
